h2_title: Yaoguai Chief - Top Takes Bottom, Bottom Takes Top
content: After defeating Top Takes Bottom, Bottom Takes Top, go up the stairs. Take out the bull guard on the right as you enter the next section, and collect the green Wisp it stands near.
